The '''Gymsnor-4''' [[Light freighter/Legends|light freighter]] was the fourth ship in the [[Gymsnor series]] produced by [[CorelliSpace]]. It resembled a flying wing, though some [[Spacer/Legends|spacers]] insultingly compared it to a [[Mynock/Legends|mynock]]. The [[Rimrunner (Gymsnor-4)|''Rimrunner'']], [[Salla Zend]]'s [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggling]] vessel, was a Gymsnor-4.

